-- South Africa Ends a 10-Year Probe Into Arms Buying Bribes, M&G Reports
-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 2010-10-15T05:10:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/south-africa-ends-a-10-year-probe-into-arms-buying-bribes-m-g-reports.html
South Africa has ended a 10-year
investigation into allegations of bribery around a deal
including the the purchase of naval ships, submarines and
airforce jets, the Mail & Guardian reported, citing the Hawks, a
government investigations body.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  